I have also being trying Symbolic API,but it is not easy for me,for example,there is no transpose operation ,but most important ,how can I use `backward()`  of `executor`?  The document seems to fail to give more details ;I saw there was an object of `grad_arrays` in the `executor`,but after implementing `backward()` I got nothing from it.

> using MXNet
> ctx=mx.gpu();
> const n_h=5000;
> const n_i=9066;
